net.gini.android.vision.network

Class GiniVisionDefaultNetworkApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.gini.android.vision.network.GiniVisionDefaultNetworkApi
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GiniVisionNetworkApi

    public class GiniVisionDefaultNetworkApi
extends java.lang.Object
implements GiniVisionNetworkApi
    Default implementation of network calls which can be performed manually from outside the Gini Vision Library (e.g. for sending feedback).

    To create an instance use the GiniVisionDefaultNetworkApi.Builder returned by the GiniVisionDefaultNetworkApi.builder() method.

    In order to easily access this implementation pass an instance of it to GiniVision.Builder#setGiniVisionNetworkApi(GiniVisionNetworkApi) when creating a GiniVision instance. You can then get the instance in your app with GiniVision#getGiniVisionNetworkApi().
